summary:
Just some sample of cool badass pages :)
 I have only a few pages left (8) !! After that, and until end of 
septembrer, I ll do...
caption:
Just some sample of cool badass pages :) I have only a few pages left (8) !! After that, and until end of septembrer, I ll do a pass to fix every drawing I can, fix the dialogues, add or remove some sequences, or adjust some sequences. I m trying to work in a very organic way and feel free to adjust the story until the end :) so exciting to work like that ( I m inspired by the way we work at Pixar, prioritizing the story over everything else, readjusting it until the end). this comicbook will be released in jan 2020 in France (hachette)

my FB page  https://www.facebook.com/RevolutionMylydy/
